data.title: Looking for a clean reasoniable priced place to sleep
data.text:
Just down the street from Knotts Berry Farm, seconds from the I 5 freeway, 3 minutes from 
CA 91 freeway.  The Coral Motel is older quaint motel the walls are sound proof my room was large had a small refrigerator and tile floor, which was great for my shedding Belgain Shepard.

Hotels start at about $70 and go up quick, weekends at the Coral Motel $50 a day.

The Coral is a friendly family run business, unfortunately I speak only english and there is a language barrier and communication takes time,

I dont know if there is a pool, there is laundry room and no problem getting on the free internet (you dont get that at motel 6).  I am going back Buena Park in a few days, you can find me at the Coral Motel every time.
